#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3837 input:3837
#: standard
msgid ""
"When claydiggers dig up earth, they leave holes in the ground. These holes "
"vanish after a while. Aqua farms can use them as ponds to grow fish in them, "
"whereas charcoal burners erect their charcoal stacks in them."
msgstr ""
"Když kopáči hlíny těží, zanechávají za sebou jámy v zemi. Tyto jámy po "
"nějakém čase zmizí. Rybí sádka mohou tyto jámy využívat jako rybníčky na "
"chov ryb, zatímco uhlíři v nich budují své milíře."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3844 input:3844
#: standard
msgid ""
"Fish are maturing in this pond. A fisher working from an aqua farm will be "
"able to catch them when they are bigger."
msgstr ""
"V tomto rybníčku dospívají ryby. Až dorostou, bude je rybář pracující na "
"rybí sádce moci vylovit."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3851 input:3851
#: standard
msgid ""
"Fish are living in this pond. A fisher working from an aqua farm can catch "
"them as food."
msgstr ""
"V tomto rybníčku již plavou ryby. Rybář pracující na rybí sádce je může "
"chytit, aby mohly posloužit jako jídlo."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3858 input:3858
#: standard
msgid ""
"A charcoal stack is burning in this earthen hole. When it has burnt down, a "
"charcoal burner will be able to gather coal from it."
msgstr ""
"V této jámě je dýmající milíř. Až nastane správný čas uhlíř z něj bude moci "
"získat uhlí."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3865 input:3865
#: standard
msgid ""
"A charcoal stack, which had been erected in this earthen hole, is ready for "
"a charcoal burner to gather coal from it."
msgstr "Milíř, který byl postaven v této jámě, je připraven na sběr uhlí."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3872 input:3872
#: standard
msgid ""
"When gardeners dig up earth, they leave holes with water in the ground. "
"These falls dry after a while or can be used by terraformer to produce new "
"soil."
msgstr ""

